creator: 300 Media Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Agency Portal helps agencies manage their businesses better by providing the essential tools for automation and efficiency, all in one system.

It is an employee scheduling software designed specifically to process information optimally and accelerate decision-making processes. The app helps you better plan your resources and employees.

Agency Portal is loaded with features including

Shift Scheduling

Timesheet Management

Invoicing

Employee Management

Compliance

Recruitment

SMS

Email System

GPS Time Clock and more
descriptionShort: Your agency’s shift management app. Choose and book shifts, manage compliance.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Update to the latest version of Agency Portal ever for:
- UI/UX improvements
- New availability - Easily set your availability on the go
- View timesheets, attach evidence and submit incident reports
- Timesheets Signature - Get timesheets signed and submitted on your phone.
- Sync with google calendar for shift updates and reminders!
- Refer a friend for job
- Bug fixes and performance improvement
